data.title: Superbad [New Blu-ray] Extended Ed, Jonah Hill , Michael Cera , Bill Hader and S 43396199217
data.meta_description:
Experience the hilarious misadventures of high school seniors Seth and Evan in the unrated extended edition of "Superbad." Directed by various talented directors and produced by Sony Pictures, this comedy film boasts a star-studded cast including Seth Rogen, Jonah Hill, Michael Cera, Bill Hader, and Chris. 

The Blu-ray disc features an aspect ratio of 1.85:1 and a runtime of 119 minutes. The movie is presented in the NTSC video format with English, French, and Spanish language options and comes with deleted scenes as a special feature. Get ready to laugh out loud with this Blu-ray edition of "Superbad" in a Blu-ray case from the comedy video genre.
